snippet.title: Hungry Dragon™ | Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Download now! http://bit.ly/hd_spc_yt_umg

Unleash fiery fury from above in Hungry Dragon, a fun and frantic action-arcade rampage where everything and everyone is on the menu!

Control ferocious dragons, flying, burning and devouring your way through a medieval realm packed with deliciously unsuspecting prey!
